\f0\fs24 \cf0 We have some awesome data structures available to us in Sass, and we\'92re able to make good use of these in our code. The first one we\'92ll look at is the if structure. Basically, we ask if something is true. If it\'92s true, then something will happen. If it\'92s false, then nothing will happen.\
